channel.title: Los Angeles Area, #2
channel.description: Hey, everyone, I can't say how sorry I am that it took so long to get these pictures up. I procrastinated for a while and then realized I couldn't find the cord that hooks my digital camera up to my computer. I've got these pictures up now.
